" To leave a comment, preface the line with a quote character and a space character. This line is an example.

" Config to load the plugin files for specific file types (filetype detection is also turned on with the plugin setting), and to load the indent file as well. 
" filetype is the name of the command, plugin and indent are specific options, and on is the boolean setting for the options
filetype plugin indent on

" Converts all tab characters to use spaces instead
set expandtab
" Sets the amount of spaces that a tab character will expand to
set tabstop=2
" Sets the amount of spaces that will be inserted when using tab in edit mode
set softtabstop=2


